              Transportation
   Departments

    The Capital Improvements Division provides design, construction, and
     project management of new City facilities and infrastructure. This
    division is responsible for the implementation and completion of the
      Transportation Decision 2000 projects, authorized by the voters.
       This section of the web site is devoted to bring you the latest
     information on projects, programs and traffic impacts in Flagstaff.

                   January 14, 2002 Transportation Update

